  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Toss broccoli florets with olive oil, salt, and pepper on a baking sheet.",
    "Roast in the oven for about 20 minutes or until tender but not mushy.",
    "Meanwhile, heat butter in a skillet over medium heat. Add minced garlic and cook for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add roasted broccoli to skillet with oregano and garlic powder. Toss gently to coat vegetables evenly.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes until heated through.",
    "Sprinkle with fresh parsley before serving."
